{"tid":950844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【商業間諜】美石油公司華籍僱員 涉偷取10億美元商業機密","createTime":"2018-12-22T00:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T02:56:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7026e4d6d2a1f6301739ad27095a0c7c1816fc4a","tid":950844,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181222/large/1545437052_61a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181222%2Flarge%2F1545437052_61a5.jpg&h=14e67cef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚鴻金(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n一名受僱於美國俄克拉何馬州一間石油公司的中國人，被控偷竊價值高達10億美元(78億港元)的商業機密。<br />\n聯邦檢察官說，35歲的譚鴻金(Hongjin Tan，音譯)在工作的研究中心盜取商業機密，再交予一間打算僱用他的中國公司。<br />\n當局說，譚鴻金涉嫌下載數以百計關於生產「下游能源市場研究開發產品的電腦檔案」。<br />\n譚鴻金是電池系統及能源儲存系統專家，根據Linkedln的資料，他去年5月起受聘於總部設於德州的跨國能源公司Phillips 66，而他之前在加州理工學院擔任訪問科學家和研究助理超過11年。譚鴻金周四被捕，下周三提堂。<br />\n美國主管國家安全的助理總檢察長德默斯(John Demers)說，偷竊知識產權損害美國公司和工人，而近日揭發的案件顯示，盜取知識產權的大都涉及中國政府和公司。<br />\n美聯社/美國Tulsa World  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181222/59058085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181222%2F59058085&d=v5ULw9joTTlZplBFgqv%2BGZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e8e185f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181222%2F59058085&h=1005aa3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181222/59058085</a>"},{"pid":"7960649c27a12bfa03a42ce6b975c4bd5fe1b94f","tid":950844,"uid":64191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:29:08.000Z","msg":"強烈要求美國再次發動麥卡錫計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8e76b247cf15a22083ea758647ab9f156fc438","tid":950844,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2